<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .box {
      position: relative;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background-color: pink;
    }
    .box::after {
      content:'After';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      right: 0;
      background-color: lightblue;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class='box'></div>
</body>
</html>
```
